text: Braulio Musso Reyes (born March 8, 1930 in Limache, Chile) is a Chilean former footballer who played for Universidad de Chile from 1951 to 1968,Profile at World Football.net and was a member of the Chile national football team at the FIFA World Cup Chile 1962, but did not play in any games.Player profile at FIFA.comTeam profile at FIFA.com ==Titles== * Universidad de Chile 1959, 1962, 1964, 1965 and 1967 (Chilean Championship) ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean footballers Category:Chile international footballers Category:Universidad de Chile footballers Category:1962 FIFA World Cup players Category:Association footballers not categorized by position
